Installation

To build this project, you need to header files for kopete and PIM.
In Debian you can install following packets:

kdepimlibs5-dev
libkopete-dev

Build:

$ mkdir build
$ cd build
$ cmake -RCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/ -DEXEC_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr -DSHARE_INSTALL_PREFIX=/usr/share/ -DDATA_INSTALL_DIR=/usr/share/kde4/kopete ..
$ make
$ make install

